cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use SPT-Txn (software or specification), please cite the software and, for the framework, the working paper below."
title: "SPT-Txn: Sovereign Policy Token Transactions"
abstract: >-
  SPT-Txn (Sovereign Policy Token Transactions) is an open-source,
  blockchain-agnostic authorization and FATF Travel Rule framework. It extends
  the IETF OAuth Transaction Tokens line with cryptographically scoped,
  attenuating capability tokens that propagate a human anchor across delegation
  chains without exposing PII, using zero-knowledge selective disclosure, an
  offline eight-step verifier, and post-quantum-hybrid key escrow.
type: software
authors:
